{"tid":1085012,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同做教育行業既人好難相處","createTime":"2019-03-30T21:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T09:51:24.000Z","uid":203889,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"27b02121048c6dbd04cb385038011a41d06666e3","tid":1085012,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:45:27.000Z","msg":"由唔同渠道識左好幾個以教野維生既人（唔計幼教）<br />\n分別以教中學/小學/補習/教樂器作為正職（唔係學生part time果隻，係搵食工）<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解佢地都好有自己果套，難聽d講就係固執<br />\n雖然佢地一般表面上好似好有親和力，懶親切<br />\n但只要討論得深入少少就發現佢地一d都唔隨和。有時候會當你係學生，覺得你要跟佢果套<br />\n<br />\n可能因為無個人諗法好難做教育？"},{"pid":"1129ffd4a74a3700d4e61020b8aedd986a72edea","tid":1085012,"uid":105066,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:52:49.000Z","msg":"慣左自己個套塞比人 愈來愈劍走偏鋒"},{"pid":"1a06d25db4cfec14ab14654bce792359bdb23331","tid":1085012,"uid":154054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:02:33.000Z","msg":"做慣左，攞教學生個套出黎同其他人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc10598a200f09886f19d812e114c1ca29b03e1","tid":1085012,"uid":123004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:15:06.000Z","msg":"慣撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垂直管理制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de83733ffee4f4dd9dc3bb068b6d434571f36a9f","tid":1085012,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"但點解唔計幼教"},{"pid":"ad28595d82c709b0fa7c36d6989bd43850f5a7cc","tid":1085012,"uid":45983,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:27:23.000Z","msg":"有次做陪審員，五個陪審員輪住宣誓，有個女教師排第三，輪到佢個陣，佢問法官：「我係教師黎，我想問可唔可以打個電話返學校先。」<br />\n<br />\n法官答：「宜家錄緊音，有咩等之後安排」<br />\n<br />\n無撚腦"},{"pid":"54f23426f7f1fc2b6c4cead45916e519b2c8ac21","tid":1085012,"uid":70584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:58:38.000Z","msg":"《孟子&bull;離婁下》曰：「人之患，在好為人師。」"},{"pid":"1ccc8339a242724e7f75971ed5be6657db2fb405","tid":1085012,"uid":70584,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得老師似係抽離唔到教訓人嘅角色，因為佢地嘅日常生活就係用硬梆梆嘅規矩、二元對立嘅思維，去教/管學生。所以對住外人，就自不然都係咁死固固<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97686497362ed1260ea25693fc22f2177843018c","tid":1085012,"uid":57848,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"教學本身都唔係一定要你跟規矩，就算呢啲所謂老師都唔係好老師。<br />\n<br />\n老師係inspire人，唔係教人做你果套"},{"pid":"7cb835eb822c1aab3f415d3a2706c843555d3181","tid":1085012,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"係麻撚煩，成日自己為是，人地做乜就錯，自己做乜就岩"},{"pid":"9dab80d8a04a20cc3cadafed01303e2cdd7e5b24","tid":1085012,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"如果佢同意你果套<br />\n等於承認比一個非做教學工作既你教返轉頭<br />\n人地仲洗靠教野搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26370b5c84d4bf398d9ce833f8f85782ba79741","tid":1085012,"uid":218865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"社工都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同親佢做野就預左佢好似點緊你做野咁<br />\n做多兩次都直接唔理佢 自己做自己野算<br />\n做完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3710d6006086bae6440a9733de8f00314a7e8c5b","tid":1085012,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de83733ffee4f4dd9dc3bb068b6d434571f36a9f","tid":1085012,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"但點解唔計幼教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"做幼教既呢個問題輕微d"},{"pid":"70b871bc58b686f13493afefc0c21015223638b9","tid":1085012,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97686497362ed1260ea25693fc22f2177843018c","tid":1085012,"uid":57848,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"教學本身都唔係一定要你跟規矩，就算呢啲所謂老師都唔係好老師。<br />\n<br />\n老師係inspire人，唔係教人做你果套"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"佢覺得自己inspire緊人呢，弊在<br />\n<br />\n例如，有個學生比較內向。佢就覺得個學生唔識朋友仔唔得，迫佢同其他人玩下。<br />\n<br />\n結果？結果就係個學生其實都未ready/同其他人本身都唔係好夾，所以先唔一齊玩。咁比你迫一迫，個內向學生就開始避佢了"},{"pid":"6b9e9773770b9b42db98b20d19adc761df719d81","tid":1085012,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26370b5c84d4bf398d9ce833f8f85782ba79741","tid":1085012,"uid":218865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"社工都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同親佢做野就預左佢好似點緊你做野咁<br />\n做多兩次都直接唔理佢 自己做自己野算<br />\n做完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"係，好同意"},{"pid":"4308dfc6a6467a46766f8f17227135679416ff33","tid":1085012,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"其實教書嘅人無咩時間留意外界嘅事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以諗野會窄啲"}]}